  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1349926180}
  m_Text: 'This eroded mountain range biome is the base biome which cover most of
    the landscape.

    For base biome, it should be place as the first child of
    Vista Manager, or have a low Order value.

    For blend mode, simply use Replace
    for all channels.'
