  m_GameObject: {fileID: 2065475598}
  m_Text: 'Flower patches appear here and there on top of existing grass.

    With
    population blend mode set to Coexist, vegetation output by this biome

    won''t
    erase what already spawned underneath.


    Same rule applied for trees and
    objects.'
